name: Dogemon
description: Dogemon is an ecosystem on the BNB blockchain that aims to deliver a Gaming and DeFi experience built around its token. Dogemon is a fantastic 3D metaverse world - Play 2 Earn Game. In this world, you can navigate your NFTs through the sections of the map, challenge various monsters , win battles to collect NFTs and $DGM. Dogemon is one of the most innovative crypto projects to date, integrating charity with cryptocurrencies for a more impactful future.
